message: Dear Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which is tailored to meet your specific needs and valued at $10000 by both parties. Considering its high quality and the benefits it offers, I would like to extend an exclusive opportunity to you at a special introductory price of $9500. This is a limited-time offer, so I hope we can discuss further to ensure you receive this exceptional value. Thank you for considering our product, and I look forward to your positive response.
